11 41-50 Megawatts of Renewable Energy: 3.5%;
12 51-60 Megawatts of Renewable Energy: 4.2%;
13 61 - 70 Megawatts of Renewable Energy: 4.9%;
14 61-80 Megawatts of Renewable Energy 5.6%;
15 81-90 Megawatts of Renewable Energy: 6.3%;
16 91 - 100 Megawatts of Renewable Energy: 7%;
17 101- 110 Megawatts of Renewable Energy: 7.7%;
18 111-120 Megawatts of Renewable Energy: 8.4%;
19 121 - 130 Megawatts of Renewable Energy: 9.1%;
20 131- 140 Megawatts of Renewable Energy: 9.8%; and
21 141-150 Megawatts of Renewable Energy: 10.5%.
22 Section 2. For purposes of this credit renewable energy shall include: Wind turbine
23 energy, Solar Panels, hydroelectric energy, Geo-Thermal Energy, and Nuclear Energy."
